#. module: theme_vehicle
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_vehicle.s_quotes_carousel_minimal
msgid ""
"\" A premier choice for luxury cars. <br/>Expert maintenance, exquisite "
"service, and utmost professionalism. \""
msgstr ""
"\" ທາງເລືອກອັນດັບໜຶ່ງສຳລັບລົດຫຼູຫຼາ. <br/>ການບຳລຸງຮັກສາໂດຍຜູ້ຊ່ຽວຊານ, ການບໍລິການທີ່ດີເລີດ, ແລະ "
"ມີຄວາມເປັນມືອາຊີບສູງສຸດ. \""

#. module: theme_vehicle
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_vehicle.s_quotes_carousel_minimal
msgid ""
"\" Outstanding service and craftsmanship! <br/>They ensure every luxury "
"vehicle is in perfect condition. \""
msgstr ""
"\" ການບໍລິການ ແລະ ຝີມືທີ່ໂດດເດັ່ນ! <br/>ພວກເຂົາຮັບປະກັນວ່າລົດຫຼູຫຼາທຸກຄັນແມ່ນຢູ່ໃນສະພາບທີ່ສົມບູນແບບ. "
"\""

#. module: theme_vehicle
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_vehicle.s_quotes_carousel_minimal
msgid ""
"\" Their service is exceptional. <br/>Premium care, top-notch quality, and "
"unparalleled attention to detail. \""
msgstr ""
"\" ການບໍລິການຂອງພວກເຂົາແມ່ນດີເລີດ. <br/>ການດູແລລະດັບພຣີມຽມ, ຄຸນນະພາບຊັ້ນຍອດ, ແລະ "
"ການເອົາໃຈໃສ່ໃນລາຍລະອຽດທີ່ບໍ່ມີໃຜທຽບໄດ້. \""

#. module: theme_vehicle
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_vehicle.s_numbers_charts
msgid "$ 2.4B"
msgstr "$ 2.4 ຕື້"

#. module: theme_vehicle
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_vehicle.s_numbers_charts
msgid ""
"75% of our clients choose to upgrade to the latest models every 3 years, "
"showcasing strong brand loyalty and trust."
msgstr ""
"75% ຂອງລູກຄ້າຂອງພວກເຮົາເລືອກທີ່ຈະອັບເກຣດເປັນລຸ້ນໃໝ່ລ່າສຸດໃນທຸກໆ 3 ປີ, "
"ເຊິ່ງສະແດງໃຫ້ເຫັນເຖິງຄວາມຈົງຮັກພັກດີ ແລະ ຄວາມເຊື່ອໝັ້ນຕໍ່ຍີ່ຫໍ້ທີ່ແຂງແກ່ນ."

#. module: theme_vehicle
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_vehicle.configurator_s_three_columns
msgid ""
"<a href=\"#\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-block mb-0 o_cc o_cc4 "
"o_translate_inline\">Configure</a>"
msgstr ""
"<a href=\"#\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-block mb-0 o_cc o_cc4 "
"o_translate_inline\">ຕັ້ງຄ່າ</a>"

